under MIT OR Apache-2.0; the crates listed here are included under their
stated licenses and we acknowledge their authors and copyright holders
accordingly.

JavaScript / npm package licenses are listed separately under the
**Frontend (npm)** tab (see `legal/npm-third-party.md`).

This file is auto-generated by `cargo about generate about.hbs` via
`scripts/regen-credits.sh`. Regenerate after dependency changes:

```
